            "text": "<p>No Wi-Fi? No SIM card? No mercy SmartSpeak Pro keeps translating with 14 powerhouse languages offline, even in tunnels, planes, remote villages, or even the moon. Never depend on a flaky app or dead signal again.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
