    "collapsible_content_7KRVQ8": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_row_Lqcw6L": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How Accurate Is The Translation? Can It Handle Real Conversations?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Yes, and then some. SmartSpeak Pro uses Google’s AI translation engine with over 97 percent accuracy in live conversations. It picks up slang, accents, and background noise with dual noise-canceling microphones. Whether you're haggling in Morocco or chatting in Tokyo, it translates fast, smooth, and natural. No robotic junk. No awkward stutters.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_3kKzE4": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Does It Work Without Wi-Fi Or A Sim Card?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Absolutely. SmartSpeak Pro translates offline in 14 essential languages. So even when you're off the grid, in a tunnel, or halfway up a mountain, you can still communicate clearly. No connection needed. Just press and talk.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_ammNtC": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How Long Does The Battery Last And Is It Easy To Use?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>You get 4 hours of active translation time and up to 72 hours on standby with one charge. And it's stupid simple to use. Just pick your two languages, press a button, and speak. No app required. No complicated setup. Just results.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_row_XTWc8c": {
          "type": "collapsible_row",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Why Should I Buy This Instead Of Using A Free Translation App Like Google Translate?",
            "icon": "question_mark",
            "row_content": "<p>Because apps lag, drain your phone, and fail when you're offline. SmartSpeak Pro gives you real time two way translation with high accuracy, noise canceling microphones, and offline support. No apps. No ads. No guessing. Just press, speak, and get answers fast. If you travel or deal with people globally, this is not a luxury. It’s a tool you need.</p>",
            "page": ""
          }
        }
      },
